column1: 9.5" Echo Your Animated  Repeating Puppy Dog Buddy
column3: Home Decor and Furniture|Childrens Corner|Stuffed Animals
column4:
Soft and cuddly puppy stuffed animal
Echo is your repeating pal
Simply press his paw speak to Echo and he'll repeat your phrase
He only repeats he will not save what you say
As he repeats he moves his head from side to side
Requires (3) "AA" batteries - included
Convenient on/off switch located on the bottom
Care instructions: hand washable with cold water mild detergent air dry

Dimensions: 9"H x 8"W x 9.5"D

column1: Window FX Christmas and Halloween Digital Seasonal Projector with Remote
column4:
This multi-functional LED projector is easy to use and perfect for displaying seasonal digital decorating content from the inside of your home
Perfect for parties entertaining your neighborhood and amazing your friends and family
Works on any size/shape window
Easily add new content for year-round decorating fun
LED lamp works for over 5 000 hours and provide superb pictures
Change in 16:9 and 4:3 aspect ratio easily
Low power consumption echo-oriented (Energy saving and environment conservation)
Multi-function interface: AV VGA SD USB HDMI

Product Specifications:
Native Resolution: 640 x 480 pixels
Support Resolution: 1920 x 1080 pixels
Imaging Unit: LCD
Lamp Model: LED
Input Voltage: 12V 2.5A
Brightness: 150 Lux
Contrast: 500:1 and lens: F=125
Image Size: 30-100 inch
Projector Distance: 1.07-3.31m
Color: 16.7K
Keystone Correction: +/- 15 degrees
Power: 30W
Built-in speaker: 1.0W x 2
Operate Method: Manual/Control
Work Temperature: -10C to 36C
Input Interface: SD USB
Output Interface: Earphone
Audio File Format: WMA MP3 ASF OGG AAC WAV
Image File Format: JPEG BMP PNG
Video File Format: AVI MOV ASF 3GP MKV RMVB MP4 DIVX FLV
Dimensions: 5.3 " x 4.4" x 2.3"

Package Contents:
Projector
Remote Control (uses (1) CR2032 3V Lithium Ion Battery - included)
Power Adapter
Preloaded SD card
Rear Projection Screen (4' x 6')
Adjustable tripod
